        <mxCell id="completeLogic" parent="awsAccount" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#f5f5f5;strokeColor=#666666;align=left;verticalAlign=top;fontSize=11;" value="&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;Lambda - Complete logic&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br&gt;1. Parse JSON body&lt;br&gt;2. Validate template_id and version_id&lt;br&gt;3. GetItem from DynamoDB&lt;br&gt;4. Assert status == PENDING&lt;br&gt;5. HeadObject on S3 using stored bucket + key&lt;br&gt;6. Verify ContentLength == expected_size&lt;br&gt;7. UpdateItem with status = UPLOADED&lt;br&gt;8. Persist uploaded_at, updated_at, actual_size, etag&lt;br&gt;9. Return status = UPLOADED" vertex="1">
